<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Jujutsu Kaisen TCG</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0e17">
<meta name="description" content="Arena de batalha de cartas contra a IA com progressão por níveis, deck e suporte PWA.">
<meta name="mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
<link rel="manifest" href="./manifest.webmanifest">
<link rel="icon" href="./icons/app-icon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@600;700;800;900&family=Rajdhani:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
    --bg-void: #05070c;
    --bg-primary: #0a0e17;
    --bg-panel: #121826;
    --bg-panel-alt: #171f30;
    --border-subtle: rgba(140, 180, 255, 0.14);
    --border-strong: rgba(140, 180, 255, 0.28);
    --accent: #3ddc84;
    --accent-dim: rgba(61, 220, 132, 0.28);
    --accent-glow: rgba(61, 220, 132, 0.45);
    --p1: #2f8fff;
    --p1-glow: rgba(47, 143, 255, 0.55);
    --p2: #ff4757;
    --p2-glow: rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.55);
    --gold: #ffd54a;
    --gold-glow: rgba(255,213,74,0.55);
    --text-primary: #e9eefb;
    --text-muted: #8592a8;
    --text-faint: #56607a;
    --font-display: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
    --font-body: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
 
    --cell-size: clamp(48px, 17vw, 100px);
    --cell-w: var(--cell-size);
    --cell-h: var(--cell-size);
    --card-w: calc(var(--cell-size) - 10px);
    --card-h: calc(var(--cell-size) - 10px);
    --opponent-card-w: calc((var(--cell-size) - 10px) / 2);
    --opponent-card-h: calc((var(--cell-size) - 10px) / 2);
}
 
*{ box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; }
 
html, body { overscroll-behavior-y: contain; }
 
body {
    background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 120% 80% at 50% -10%, rgba(61,220,132,0.08), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 100% 60% at 100% 100%, rgba(47,143,255,0.06), transparent 60%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-void) 0%, var(--bg-primary) 100%);
    background-attachment: fixed;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 20px 10px 60px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    min-height: 100vh;
    position: relative;
}
 
body::before{
    content: "";
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(140,180,255,0.035) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(140,180,255,0.035) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 42px 42px;
    mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 20%, black, transparent 75%);
    z-index: 0;
}
 
body > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
 
h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 6vw, 40px);
    letter-spacing: clamp(4px, 2vw, 10px);
    margin: 0 0 4px;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, var(--accent) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    text-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--accent-glow);
}
 
.subtitle{
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-align: center;
}
 
h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-align: center;
    margin: 24px 0 12px;
    position: relative;
}
 
h2::after{
    content: "";
    display: block;
    width: 46px;
    height: 2px;
    margin: 8px auto 0;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--accent), transparent);
    opacity: 0.6;
}
 
#turnBanner{
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(12px, 3vw, 15px);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 10px 26px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    background: var(--bg-panel);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    transition: color 0.3s, border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
}
#turnBanner .dot{
    width: 9px; height: 9px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: currentColor;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px currentColor;
    animation: turnPulse 1.4s ease-in-out infinite;
}
#turnBanner.p1-turn{ color: var(--p1); border-color: rgba(47,143,255,0.4); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(47,143,255,0.15); }
#turnBanner.p2-turn{ color: var(--p2); border-color: rgba(255,71,87,0.4); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,71,87,0.15); }
#turnBanner.thinking{ opacity: 0.75; }
 
@keyframes turnPulse{
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
    50% { transform: scale(1.5); opacity: 0.5; }
}
 
#boardContainer {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding: 16px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02), transparent);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 16px;
    max-width: 100%;
}
 
#board {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, var(--cell-w));
    grid-template-rows: repeat(5, var(--cell-h));
    gap: 6px;
}

.cell.center-cell {
    border-color: rgba(255, 213, 74, 0.45);
    background:
        radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,213,74,0.1), transparent 70%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.015), transparent 60%),
        var(--bg-panel);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,213,74,0.2);
}
.cell.center-cell:empty::after {
    content: "";
    font-size: calc(var(--cell-size) * 0.36);
    opacity: 0.3;
    pointer-events: none;
}
.cell.center-cell.valid-target {
    border-color: var(--gold);
}
.cell.center-cell.valid-target-override {
    border-color: var(--p2);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,71,87,0.4), 0 0 16px rgba(255,71,87,0.2);
    animation: validPulse 1.6s ease-in-out infinite;
}
 
.cell {
    width: var(--cell-w);
    height: var(--cell-h);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.015), transparent 60%),
        var(--bg-panel);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    position: relative;
}
.cell:hover{
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px var(--accent-dim), 0 0 16px rgba(61,220,132,0.12);
}
 
.cell.valid-target{
    border-color: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,213,74,0.4), 0 0 16px rgba(255,213,74,0.18);
    animation: validPulse 1.6s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes validPulse{
    0%, 100% { box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,213,74,0.4), 0 0 10px rgba(255,213,74,0.12); }
    50% { box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,213,74,0.7), 0 0 22px rgba(255,213,74,0.3); }
}
 
.card {
    width: var(--card-w);
    height: var(--card-h);
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    border-radius: 8px;
    position: relative;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    cursor: pointer;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, border-color 0.4s ease;
}
.card:hover{
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
}
 
.card::before{
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.16) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 30%, transparent 55%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
}
 
.card::after{
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
    height: 46%;
    background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.55), transparent);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
}
 
.card.selected {
    border-color: var(--gold) !important;
    border-width: 3px !important;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(255,213,74,0.25), 0 0 18px rgba(255,213,74,0.45) !important;
}
 
.card.just-placed{
    animation: cardPlace 0.32s cubic-bezier(.2,1.4,.4,1);
}
@keyframes cardPlace{
    0% { transform: scale(0.35) translateY(10px); opacity: 0; }
    60% { transform: scale(1.08); opacity: 1; }
    100% { transform: scale(1); }
}
 
.card.capturing{
    animation: captureFlip 0.55s ease-in-out;
    z-index: 5;
}
@keyframes captureFlip{
    0% { transform: scaleX(1); filter: brightness(1); }
    45% { transform: scaleX(0.05); filter: brightness(1.6); }
    55% { transform: scaleX(0.05); filter: brightness(1.6); }
    100% { transform: scaleX(1); filter: brightness(1); }
}

.card.destroyed-zero{
    animation: shatterOut 0.5s ease-in forwards;
    z-index: 5;
    pointer-events: none;
}
@keyframes shatterOut{
    0% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg); opacity: 1; filter: brightness(1) saturate(1); }
    30% { transform: scale(1.08) rotate(-3deg); filter: brightness(1.8) saturate(0); }
    100% { transform: scale(0.2) rotate(12deg); opacity: 0; filter: brightness(0.4) saturate(0); }
}

.power-ring{
    position: absolute;
    inset: -4px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 2px solid var(--accent);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 6;
    animation: ringPulse 0.7s ease-out forwards;
}
.power-ring.push{ border-color: #ff9f4a; }
.power-ring.drain{ border-color: #ff5b7a; }
.power-ring.boost{ border-color: #6bff9f; }
.power-ring.freeze{ border-color: #4fc3f7; }
@keyframes ringPulse{
    0% { transform: scale(0.85); opacity: 1; box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 currentColor; }
    100% { transform: scale(1.5); opacity: 0; box-shadow: 0 0 24px 6px currentColor; }
}
 
.card.boost-glow{
    animation: boostGlow 0.9s ease-in-out;
}
@keyframes boostGlow{
    0% { box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.45); }
    40% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(107,255,159,0.5), 0 0 24px rgba(107,255,159,0.55); }
    100% { box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.45); }
}
 
.card.drain-hit{
    animation: drainShake 0.5s ease-in-out;
}
@keyframes drainShake{
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); filter: brightness(1); }
    20% { transform: translateX(-3px); filter: brightness(0.65); }
    40% { transform: translateX(3px); }
    60% { transform: translateX(-2px); }
    80% { transform: translateX(2px); }
}
.card.drain-source{
    animation: boostGlow 0.6s ease-in-out;
}
 
.card.frozen{
    border-color: #4fc3f7 !important;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(79,195,247,0.4), inset 0 0 20px rgba(79,195,247,0.15) !important;
    animation: freezePulse 1.2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes freezePulse{
    0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(79,195,247,0.3), inset 0 0 15px rgba(79,195,247,0.1); }
    50% { box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(79,195,247,0.5), inset 0 0 30px rgba(79,195,247,0.2); }
}
.card.frozen::after{
    content: "❄️";
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-size: 20px;
    z-index: 5;
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(79,195,247,0.8);
    opacity: 0.7;
}
 
.float-num{
    position: absolute;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 15px;
    z-index: 20;
    pointer-events: none;
    animation: floatUp 0.9s ease-out forwards;
    text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
}
.float-num.pos{ color: #6bff9f; }
.float-num.neg{ color: #ff6b6b; }
.float-num.freeze-float{ color: #4fc3f7; }
@keyframes floatUp{
    0% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
    100% { transform: translateY(-32px); opacity: 0; }
}
 
.card.pushing{
    transition: transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(.3,.9,.4,1);
    z-index: 6;
}
 
.values {
    position: absolute;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 12px;
    z-index: 3;
    color: #ffffff;
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.9), 0 0 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
    transition: color 0.3s;
    line-height: 1;
    padding: 0;
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 16px;
}
 
.value-normal { color: #ffffff; }
.value-decreased { color: #ff6b6b; }
.value-increased { color: #6bff9f; }
.value-frozen { color: #4fc3f7; }
 
.top { 
    top: 3px; 
    left: 50%; 
    transform: translateX(-50%);
}
.right { 
    top: 50%; 
    right: 4px; 
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    left: auto;
}
.bottom { 
    bottom: 3px; 
    left: 50%; 
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    top: auto;
}
.left { 
    top: 50%; 
    left: 4px; 
    transform: translateY(-50%);
}
 
.card-level {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 6px;
    right: 6px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 10px;
    z-index: 3;
    color: #ffd54a;
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255,213,74,0.6), 0 0 20px rgba(255,213,74,0.3), 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
    line-height: 1;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    padding: 0 4px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,213,74,0.2);
}

.card.domain-card {
    border-color: rgba(200, 120, 255, 0.6);
    box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(200, 120, 255, 0.4), 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
}
.domain-refino {
    position: absolute;
    top: 6px;
    left: 6px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 10px;
    z-index: 3;
    color: #d9a9ff;
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(200,120,255,0.6), 0 0 20px rgba(200,120,255,0.3), 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
    line-height: 1;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    padding: 0 4px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,120,255,0.35);
}
.card-modal-image .domain-refino {
    top: 6px;
    left: 6px;
    font-size: 20px;
    padding: 0 8px;
    z-index: 4;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,120,255,0.4);
}
.domain-hint {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: center;
}
 
#handsWrapper{
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 760px;
    gap: 4px;
}
 
.hand-section{
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 6px 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s, filter 0.3s;
}
.hand-section.inactive{
    opacity: 0.55;
    filter: grayscale(0.25);
}
.hand-section .hand-title{
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
}
.hand-section .waiting-tag{
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 999px;
}
 
.opponent-count {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    background: var(--bg-panel-alt);
    padding: 2px 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
}
 
#playerCards, #opponentCards {
    margin-top: 4px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 720px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    padding: 12px 6px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
}
 
#playerCards::-webkit-scrollbar,
#opponentCards::-webkit-scrollbar { height: 6px; }
 
#playerCards::-webkit-scrollbar-track,
#opponentCards::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
    background: var(--bg-panel);
    border-radius: 4px;
}
 
#playerCards::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb,
#opponentCards::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 4px;
}
 
.owner1 { border-color: var(--p1); box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--p1-glow), 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.45); }
.owner2 { border-color: var(--p2); box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--p2-glow), 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.45); }
.owner1.selected, .owner2.selected { box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(255,213,74,0.25), 0 0 18px rgba(255,213,74,0.45) !important; }
 
.card.card-hidden {
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);
    box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
}
.card.card-hidden::before {
    content: "?";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        45deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 10px,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 10px,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 20px
    );
    z-index: 2;
}
.card.card-hidden .values,
.card.card-hidden .card-level {
    opacity: 0.15;
    filter: blur(2px);
}
.card.card-hidden::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
}
 
.card.opponent-hand {
    width: var(--opponent-card-w);
    height: var(--opponent-card-h);
}
.card.opponent-hand .values {
    font-size: 8px;
}
.card.opponent-hand .card-level {
    font-size: 7px;
    bottom: 3px;
    right: 3px;
    padding: 0 2px;
}
.card.opponent-hand .top { top: 1px; }
.card.opponent-hand .right { right: 1px; }
.card.opponent-hand .bottom { bottom: 1px; }
.card.opponent-hand .left { left: 1px; }
.card.opponent-hand.card-hidden::before {
    font-size: 18px;
}
.card.opponent-hand.card-hidden .values,
.card.opponent-hand.card-hidden .card-level {
    opacity: 0.1;
    filter: blur(1px);
}
 
.scoreboard{
    margin-top: 18px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 18px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 17px;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    background: var(--bg-panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 999px;
}
.scoreboard .tag{
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 14px;
}
.scoreboard .tag.p1{ color: var(--p1); background: rgba(47,143,255,0.12); }
.scoreboard .tag.p2{ color: var(--p2); background: rgba(255,71,87,0.12); }
.scoreboard .vs{ color: var(--text-faint); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 3px; }
 
#winnerBox {
    margin-top: 22px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-align: center;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
}
 
#toastContainer{
    position: fixed;
    top: 80px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    z-index: 500;
    align-items: center;
    pointer-events: none;
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 380px;
}
.toast{
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    background: rgba(10,14,23,0.92);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    padding: 9px 18px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    text-align: center;
    animation: toastIn 0.25s ease, toastOut 0.3s ease 1.5s forwards;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    max-width: 100%;
}
.toast.gold{ border-color: rgba(255,213,74,0.5); color: var(--gold); }
.toast.p1{ border-color: rgba(47,143,255,0.5); color: var(--p1); }
.toast.p2{ border-color: rgba(255,71,87,0.5); color: var(--p2); }
.toast.freeze{ border-color: rgba(79,195,247,0.5); color: #4fc3f7; }
@keyframes toastIn{
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
@keyframes toastOut{
    from { opacity: 1; }
    to { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-8px); }
}
 
.card-modal-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background: rgba(3,5,9,0.86);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    z-index: 1000;
    opacity: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    transition: opacity 0.25s, visibility 0.25s;
    padding: 16px;
}
 
.card-modal-overlay.active { opacity: 1; visibility: visible; }
 
.card-modal {
    background: var(--bg-panel);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px;
    width: 420px;
    max-width: 100%;
    max-height: 90vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), 0 0 40px rgba(61,220,132,0.08);
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
}
 
.card-modal-close {
    position: absolute;
    top: 12px;
    right: 12px;
    background: var(--bg-panel-alt);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    font-size: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    z-index: 10;
}
.card-modal-close:hover{ background: var(--p2); border-color: var(--p2); }

/* Reserva espaço para o X (que fica em absolute, sobre o fluxo normal) para o título
   nunca ficar embaixo dele, mesmo em telas estreitas onde o texto centralizado
   chegaria perto da borda direita do modal. */
.card-modal-close ~ .panel-title {
    max-width: calc(100% - 84px);
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    text-align: center;
}

.card-modal-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    width: 100%;
}
 
.card-modal-image {
    width: 280px;
    height: 280px;
    max-width: 100%;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 3px solid var(--p1);
    box-shadow: 0 0 24px var(--p1-glow);
    position: relative;
    flex-shrink: 0;
}
 
.card-modal-image .values {
    position: absolute;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 22px;
    z-index: 3;
    color: #ffffff;
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.9), 0 0 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
    line-height: 1;
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 30px;
}
.card-modal-image .values.top { 
    top: 6px; 
    left: 50%; 
    transform: translateX(-50%);
}
.card-modal-image .values.right { 
    top: 50%; 
    right: 8px; 
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    left: auto;
}
.card-modal-image .values.bottom { 
    bottom: 6px; 
    left: 50%; 
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    top: auto;
}
.card-modal-image .values.left { 
    top: 50%; 
    left: 8px; 
    transform: translateY(-50%);
}
.card-modal-image .value-normal { color: #ffffff; }
.card-modal-image .value-decreased { color: #ff6b6b; }
.card-modal-image .value-increased { color: #6bff9f; }
.card-modal-image .value-frozen { color: #4fc3f7; }
 
.card-modal-image .card-level {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 6px;
    right: 6px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 20px;
    z-index: 4;
    color: #ffd54a;
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255,213,74,0.6), 0 0 20px rgba(255,213,74,0.3), 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
    line-height: 1;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    padding: 0 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,213,74,0.3);
}
 
.card-modal-info {
    text-align: center;
    width: 100%;
}
 
.card-modal-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-align: center;
}
 
.card-modal-power {
    background: var(--bg-panel-alt);
    padding: 14px 18px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 4px;
}
 
.card-modal-power-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-align: center;
}
 
.card-modal-power-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: center;
}

.shadow-modal { width: 660px; }
.shadow-modal-hint { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 4px 0 16px; text-align: center; }
.shadow-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(116px, 1fr)); gap: 14px; width: 100%; max-height: 65vh; overflow-y: auto; padding: 4px; }
.shadow-option { background: var(--bg-panel-alt); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px; transition: border-color 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s, transform 0.12s; }
.shadow-option .card { --card-w: 96px; --card-h: 96px; cursor: inherit; }
.shadow-option[data-choosable="true"] { cursor: pointer; }
.shadow-option[data-choosable="true"]:hover { border-color: var(--accent); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--accent-dim); transform: translateY(-2px); }
.shadow-option .shadow-name { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: var(--text-primary); text-align: center; line-height: 1.2; }
.shadow-option.mahoraga { border-color: rgba(255,71,87,0.4); background: rgba(255,71,87,0.06); }
.shadow-option .shadow-warn { font-size: 10px; color: var(--p2); letter-spacing: 0.3px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.3; }
 
.screen { width: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
.hidden { display: none !important; }
#mainMenu { max-width: 980px; min-height: calc(100vh - 80px); justify-content: center; gap: 18px; }
.menu-panel, .deck-panel, .levels-panel, .tutorial-panel { width: min(940px, 96vw); background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.035), rgba(255,255,255,0.01)); border: 1px solid var(--border-strong); border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px; box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.38); }
.tutorial-panel { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; }
.tutorial-step { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px 18px; }
.tutorial-step-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 800; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin: 0 0 8px; }
.tutorial-step p { margin: 0; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }
.tutorial-step p + p { margin-top: 8px; }
.tutorial-visual-row { display: flex; gap: 28px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.tutorial-visual-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
.tutorial-visual-card .card { --card-w: 96px; --card-h: 96px; cursor: default; }
.tutorial-visual-card .card:hover { transform: none; box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.45); }
.tutorial-visual-label { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.4; }
.tutorial-visual-label span { display: block; margin-top: 3px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-faint); }
.tutorial-board-preview { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 22px); grid-template-rows: repeat(5, 22px); gap: 3px; justify-content: center; margin: 4px auto 14px; }
.tutorial-cell { width: 22px; height: 22px; border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); border-radius: 3px; background: var(--bg-panel); }
.tutorial-cell.center-cell { border-color: rgba(255, 213, 74, 0.6); background: rgba(255, 213, 74, 0.15); }
.menu-actions { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(180px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; margin-top: 16px; }
.menu-btn, .panel-btn, .card-action-btn { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-primary); background: var(--bg-panel); border: 1px solid var(--border-strong); border-radius: 8px; padding: 13px 16px; cursor: pointer; transition: border-color 0.18s, color 0.18s, transform 0.12s, box-shadow 0.18s; }
.menu-btn:hover, .panel-btn:hover, .card-action-btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--accent-dim); }
.menu-btn:active, .panel-btn:active, .card-action-btn:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
.menu-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 700; }
#installBtn { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
.install-hint { min-height: 18px; margin-top: 12px; color: var(--text-faint); font-weight: 700; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.4px; }
.panel-topbar { width: min(940px, 96vw); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.panel-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); }
.deck-status {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(255, 213, 74, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 213, 74, 0.35);
    padding: 8px 18px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(255, 213, 74, 0.15);
}
.deck-status.deck-status-full {
    color: var(--p2);
    background: rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.18);
}
.card-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(112px, 1fr)); gap: 14px; width: 100%; }
.manage-card { background: var(--bg-panel); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; align-items: center; min-height: 150px; transition: all 0.2s; }
.manage-card .card { --card-w: 84px; --card-h: 84px; cursor: pointer; }
.manage-card-name { width: 100%; min-height: 32px; color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 700; text-align: center; line-height: 1.1; }
.card-action-btn { width: 100%; padding: 8px 10px; font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
.card-action-btn.remove { border-color: rgba(255,71,87,0.45); color: var(--p2); }
.card-action-btn.add { border-color: rgba(61,220,132,0.45); color: var(--accent); }
.manage-card.locked { opacity: 0.55; filter: grayscale(0.6); cursor: not-allowed; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
.manage-card.locked .card { filter: brightness(0.4); }
.lock-tag { font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 700; font-size: 11.5px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; color: var(--gold); text-align: center; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 6px; }
.lock-tag::before { content: "🔒"; font-size: 14px; }
.deck-columns { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
.deck-column-title { margin: 0 0 12px; color: var(--text-muted); font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
.deck-column-title .badge { font-size: 11px; background: var(--bg-panel-alt); padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 999px; color: var(--text-faint); }
.deck-column-title .badge.in-deck { background: rgba(61,220,132,0.2); color: var(--accent); }
.deck-column-title .badge.available { background: rgba(47,143,255,0.2); color: var(--p1); }
.deck-column-title .badge.locked { background: rgba(255,213,74,0.15); color: var(--gold); }
 
.manage-card.in-deck { border-color: var(--accent); background: rgba(61,220,132,0.06); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(61,220,132,0.06); }
.manage-card.in-deck .card { border-color: var(--accent); box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(61,220,132,0.15); }
.manage-card.available { border-color: var(--p1); border-style: dashed; background: rgba(47,143,255,0.04); }
.manage-card.available .card { border-color: var(--p1); }
 
.card-status-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -6px;
    right: -6px;
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    z-index: 10;
    border: 2px solid var(--bg-panel);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
}
.card-status-badge.in-deck { background: var(--accent); color: #000; }
.card-status-badge.available { background: var(--p1); color: #fff; }
.card-status-badge.locked { background: var(--gold); color: #000; }
 
.empty-state {
    color: var(--text-faint);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 30px 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    border: 1px dashed var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 8px;
    width: 100%;
}
 
.deck-hint {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 8px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-top: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
}
 
#gameScreen { padding-bottom: 10px; padding-top: 6px; }
.game-nav { margin-bottom: 12px; }
 
#gameTopBar{
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 8px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto 10px;
}
#gameTopBar .scoreboard{
    margin-top: 0;
}
#turnBanner{ display: none; }
 
.settings-btn{
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 19px;
    background: var(--bg-panel);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 50%;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s, transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.2s;
}
.settings-btn:hover{
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--accent-dim);
}
.settings-btn:active{ transform: scale(0.92); }
 
.settings-modal{
    width: 300px;
    max-width: 100%;
    gap: 10px;
}
.settings-modal .panel-title{ margin-bottom: 6px; }
.settings-modal-actions{
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    width: 100%;
    gap: 10px;
}
#settingsModal #restartBtn,
#settingsModal #gameMenuBtn{
    width: 100%;
    height: 48px;
    flex: 0 0 48px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0 16px;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    line-height: 1;
}
 
#winnerOverlay .card-modal{
    width: 380px;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
}
#winnerOverlay #winnerBox{ margin-top: 0; }
#winnerOverlay #postMatchActions{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}
 
.hand-section h2{ margin: 6px 0 4px; }
#gameScreen #boardContainer{ padding: 10px; margin: 0 auto; }
 
@media (max-width: 600px) {
    #gameTopBar{ gap: 6px; }
    .settings-btn{ width: 36px; height: 36px; font-size: 16px; }
}
 
.level-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 14px; width: 100%; }
.level-btn {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 4px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    background: var(--bg-panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s, transform 0.12s;
}
.level-btn .level-num { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; }
.level-btn .level-tag { font-size: 9.5px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-faint); font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 700; }
.level-btn:hover:not(.locked){ border-color: var(--accent); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--accent-dim); transform: translateY(-2px); }
.level-btn:active:not(.locked){ transform: scale(0.96); }
.level-btn.completed{ border-color: var(--gold); box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(255,213,74,0.25); }
.level-btn.completed .level-tag{ color: var(--gold); }
.level-btn.locked{ opacity: 0.4; filter: grayscale(0.7); cursor: not-allowed; }
.level-progress { width: 100%; text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
 
@media (max-width: 760px) {
    .menu-actions { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .menu-panel, .deck-panel, .levels-panel, .tutorial-panel { padding: 16px; }
    .card-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(98px, 1fr)); gap: 10px; }
    .level-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
    .deck-column-title { font-size: 12px; }
}
 
@media (max-width: 600px) {
    body { margin-top: 4px; padding: 14px 5px 40px; }
    #boardContainer { gap: 10px; padding: 10px; }
    .values { font-size: 11px; }
    .top { top: 2px; }
    .right { right: 2px; }
    .bottom { bottom: 2px; }
    .left { left: 2px; }
    .card-level { font-size: 9px; bottom: 4px; right: 4px; padding: 0 3px; }
    #playerCards, #opponentCards { gap: 8px; margin-top: 4px; padding: 10px 3px; }
    h2 { font-size: 13px; margin: 16px 0 8px; }
    #controls { width: 100%; }
    #restartBtn { width: 90%; max-width: 300px; font-size: 14px; }
    .scoreboard{ font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 16px; gap: 12px; }
    .card-modal { padding: 18px; width: 95%; }
    .card-modal-image { width: 200px; height: 200px; }
    .card-modal-image .values { font-size: 16px; min-width: 20px; }
    .card-modal-image .values.top { top: 4px; }
    .card-modal-image .values.right { right: 4px; }
    .card-modal-image .values.bottom { bottom: 4px; }
    .card-modal-image .values.left { left: 4px; }
    .card-modal-image .card-level { font-size: 16px; bottom: 4px; right: 4px; padding: 0 6px; }
    .card-modal-name { font-size: 18px; }
    .card-modal-power-desc { font-size: 12px; }
    .settings-modal{ width: 260px; }
    .panel-title { font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
}
 
@media (max-width: 380px) {
    .values { font-size: 9px; }
    .top { top: 1px; }
    .right { right: 1px; }
    .bottom { bottom: 1px; }
    .left { left: 1px; }
    .card-level { font-size: 8px; bottom: 3px; right: 3px; padding: 0 2px; }
    h2 { font-size: 12px; }
    #playerCards, #opponentCards { gap: 5px; }
}
 
@media (max-height: 480px) and (orientation: landscape) {
    body{ padding-top: 8px; }
    h1{ font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 4px; margin-bottom: 0; }
    .subtitle{ margin-bottom: 8px; }
    #controls{ margin-bottom: 8px; }
    #turnBanner{ margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 6px 18px; }
    :root{
        --cell-size: clamp(44px, 9.5vw, 78px);
    }
    h2{ margin: 10px 0 6px; }
}
 
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    *, *::before, *::after {
        animation-duration: 0.001ms !important;
        animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
        transition-duration: 0.001ms !important;
    }
}
 
</style>
</head>
<body>
 
<section id="mainMenu" class="screen">
    <h1>Jujutsu TCG</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">Arena de Batalha de Cartas</div>
    <div class="menu-panel">
        <div class="menu-row"><span id="menuDeckInfo">Deck: 0 cartas</span><span id="menuLevelInfo">Nível máximo: 1</span></div>
        <div class="menu-actions"><button id="playBtn" class="menu-btn" type="button">Jogar</button><button id="deckBtn" class="menu-btn" type="button">Deck</button><button id="tutorialBtn" class="menu-btn" type="button">Tutorial</button><button id="installBtn" class="menu-btn hidden" type="button">Instalar app</button></div>
        <div id="installStatus" class="install-hint" aria-live="polite"></div>
    </div>
</section>
 
<section id="levelScreen" class="screen hidden">
    <div class="panel-topbar"><div><div class="panel-title">Selecionar Nível</div></div><button id="levelBackBtn" class="panel-btn" type="button">Voltar</button></div>
    <div class="levels-panel">
        <div id="levelProgress" class="level-progress"></div>
        <div id="levelGrid" class="level-grid"></div>
    </div>
</section>
 
<section id="deckScreen" class="screen hidden">
    <div class="panel-topbar"><div><div class="panel-title">Editar Deck</div><div id="deckCount" class="deck-status">0 cartas</div></div><button id="deckBackBtn" class="panel-btn" type="button">Voltar</button></div>
    <div class="deck-panel deck-columns">
        <div>
            <div class="deck-column-title">📋 No Deck <span class="badge in-deck" id="inDeckCount">0</span></div>
            <div id="activeDeckList" class="card-grid"></div>
            <div id="activeDeckEmpty" class="empty-state">Nenhuma carta no deck</div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div class="deck-column-title">📦 Disponíveis <span class="badge available" id="availableCount">0</span></div>
            <div id="collectionList" class="card-grid"></div>
            <div id="collectionEmpty" class="empty-state">Todas as cartas disponíveis estão no deck</div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div class="deck-column-title">🔒 Bloqueadas <span class="badge locked" id="lockedCount">0</span></div>
            <div id="lockedList" class="card-grid"></div>
            <div id="lockedEmpty" class="empty-state">Nenhuma carta bloqueada</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="tutorialScreen" class="screen hidden">
    <div class="panel-topbar"><div><div class="panel-title">Tutorial</div></div><button id="tutorialBackBtn" class="panel-btn" type="button">Voltar</button></div>
    <div class="tutorial-panel">
        <div class="tutorial-step">
            <div class="tutorial-step-title">🎯 Objetivo</div>
            <p>Cada partida é disputada num tabuleiro. Você e o oponente se revezam colocando cartas nas casas vazias, tentando capturar as cartas um do outro. Quem terminar a partida controlando mais cartas no tabuleiro vence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tutorial-step">
            <div class="tutorial-step-title">🃏 Os dois tipos de carta</div>
            <div class="tutorial-visual-row">
                <div class="tutorial-visual-card">
                    <div id="tutorialCharCardSlot"></div>
                    <div class="tutorial-visual-label">Feiticeiro<br><span>4 atributos (topo, direita, baixo, esquerda) + nível no canto</span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="tutorial-visual-card">
                    <div id="tutorialDomainCardSlot"></div>
                    <div class="tutorial-visual-label">Expansão de Domínio<br><span>Sem atributos: refino no canto superior + nível no canto</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>Cartas de Feiticeiro são a maioria do seu deck e são elas que capturam e são capturadas. Expansões de Domínio são um tipo raro e especial: em vez de atributos, têm um número de <strong>refino</strong> e afetam o tabuleiro inteiro quando jogadas.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tutorial-step">
            <div class="tutorial-step-title">🗺️ O tabuleiro</div>
            <div id="tutorialBoardPreview" class="tutorial-board-preview"></div>
            <p>O tabuleiro tem 5×5 casas (25 no total). A casa bem no meio, destacada em dourado, é reservada exclusivamente para Expansões de Domínio: nenhuma carta de personagem pode ser jogada nela, e nenhuma Expansão de Domínio pode ser jogada em outro lugar.</p>
            <p>Só pode existir uma Expansão de Domínio em campo por vez. Para jogar outra por cima de uma que já está lá, o refino da nova precisa ser igual ou maior — isso destrói a anterior (que não pode mais ser usada naquela partida) e o efeito da nova passa a valer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tutorial-step">
            <div class="tutorial-step-title">▶️ Como jogar sua vez</div>
            <p>Na sua vez, toque numa carta da sua mão para selecioná-la e depois toque numa casa vazia válida do tabuleiro para jogá-la ali. Os jogadores se revezam turno a turno até o fim da partida.</p>
            <p>Se você ficar sem cartas na mão antes do oponente, ele continua jogando sozinho até a mão dele também esvaziar — você não perde a vez, simplesmente não tem mais nada pra jogar.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tutorial-step">
            <div class="tutorial-step-title">⚔️ Como capturar</div>
            <p>Toda carta de feiticeiro tem 4 números: um em cima, um embaixo, um à esquerda e um à direita. Ao colocar sua carta ao lado de uma carta inimiga, o número do seu lado voltado para ela é comparado com o número do lado dela voltado para você.</p>
            <p>Se o seu número for maior, você captura aquela carta — ela passa a ser sua, mesmo continuando na mesma casa do tabuleiro. Uma única jogada pode capturar várias cartas inimigas ao mesmo tempo, se houver mais de uma adjacente.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tutorial-step">
            <div class="tutorial-step-title">💥 Cartas destruídas</div>
            <p>Alguns efeitos reduzem os atributos de uma carta (como poderes que cortam valores pela metade ou diminuem um atributo). Se os 4 números de uma carta chegarem a zero ao mesmo tempo, ela é <strong>destruída</strong>: sai do tabuleiro imediatamente e não pode ser usada de novo naquela partida, nem por você nem pelo oponente.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tutorial-step">
            <div class="tutorial-step-title">✨ Cartas especiais</div>
            <p>Muitas cartas de personagem têm poderes únicos que ativam automaticamente (ou pedem uma escolha) assim que entram em campo. Para conhecer o poder de cada carta, toque duas vezes (ou dê um duplo clique) nela para abrir os detalhes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tutorial-step">
            <div class="tutorial-step-title">🏆 Fim de partida</div>
            <p>A partida termina em qualquer uma destas duas situações, o que acontecer primeiro:</p>
            <p>• Todas as casas do tabuleiro (menos a central) ficam ocupadas;</p>
            <p>• Nenhum dos dois jogadores tem mais cartas na mão para jogar, mesmo com casas vazias sobrando.</p>
            <p>Quando a partida acaba, vence quem tiver mais cartas suas no tabuleiro naquele momento. Empate é possível.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tutorial-step">
            <div class="tutorial-step-title">🧩 Montando seu deck</div>
            <p>Na tela de Deck você escolhe quais cartas desbloqueadas vão para o seu baralho. Cada carta tem um nível, e a soma dos níveis do seu deck não pode passar do limite mostrado na tela.</p>
            <p>Seu deck precisa ter pelo menos 1 carta de personagem para você poder entrar numa partida — um deck só com Expansões de Domínio não é suficiente, já que elas sozinhas não enchem o tabuleiro.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<main id="gameScreen" class="screen hidden">
